  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fred's car breaks down in the middle of a forest, forcing him to seek help. But he soon discovers that something else is going on. Your goal in this text-based choice game is to help the protagonist survive until he uncovers the mysteries of this place and reunites with his daughter, Susan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/546e04c699e0f59831f625a5977a5fee.avif?t=1764620237\" width=598 height=332 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>6+ DIFFERENT ENDINGS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many paths that you can choose and lead to more than 6 different endings. Some good and others bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/a0bb4e669f71533fe96477d1ab573055.avif?t=1764620237\" width=598 height=336 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>IMMERSIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many places to visit with images of all the regions of the game. Gameplay full of sounds for better fill the ambience and what is happening at the momment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVAL MECHANICS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are controlling a person, keep that in mind if you want Fred to survive his journey. With health and hunger meters, mainten then filled up by using itens from your inventory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/b0220e825b3dfd6778fa99a9a1424c49.poster.avif?t=1764620237\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/b0220e825b3dfd6778fa99a9a1424c49.webm?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/b0220e825b3dfd6778fa99a9a1424c49.mp4?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FULL TRANSLATION TO ENGLISH, SPANISH AND PORTUGUESE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains full translation for both english, spanish and brazilian portuguese. And plans for even more languages in the future! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/33238d3aa13a05a1fb58cfb22975123c.poster.avif?t=1764620237\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/33238d3aa13a05a1fb58cfb22975123c.webm?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/33238d3aa13a05a1fb58cfb22975123c.mp4?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>STORY:</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fred's car breaks down in the middle of a forest, forcing him to seek help. But he soon discovers that something else is going on. Your goal in this text-based choice game is to help the protagonist survive until he uncovers the mysteries of this place and reunites with his daughter, Susan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/546e04c699e0f59831f625a5977a5fee.avif?t=1764620237\" width=598 height=332 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>6+ DIFFERENT ENDINGS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are many paths that you can choose and lead to more than 6 different endings. Some good and others bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/a0bb4e669f71533fe96477d1ab573055.avif?t=1764620237\" width=598 height=336 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>IMMERSIVE GAMEPLAY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Many places to visit with images of all the regions of the game. Gameplay full of sounds for better fill the ambience and what is happening at the momment. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SURVIVAL MECHANICS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are controlling a person, keep that in mind if you want Fred to survive his journey. With health and hunger meters, mainten then filled up by using itens from your inventory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/b0220e825b3dfd6778fa99a9a1424c49.poster.avif?t=1764620237\" width=600 height=332 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/b0220e825b3dfd6778fa99a9a1424c49.webm?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/b0220e825b3dfd6778fa99a9a1424c49.mp4?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FULL TRANSLATION TO ENGLISH, SPANISH AND PORTUGUESE</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game contains full translation for both english, spanish and brazilian portuguese. And plans for even more languages in the future! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/33238d3aa13a05a1fb58cfb22975123c.poster.avif?t=1764620237\" width=600 height=334 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/33238d3aa13a05a1fb58cfb22975123c.webm?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3186200/extras/33238d3aa13a05a1fb58cfb22975123c.mp4?t=1764620237\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
